Host,Stream,Sell,is,a,video,hosting,and,streaming,solution,for,providing,secure,access,to,your,videos,Use,the,platform,to,upload,encode,and,securely,store,your,videos,in,the,cloud,Access,to,your,videos,is,permitted,using,simple,API,calls,in,your,application,The,API,enables,you,to,send,requests,and,retrieve,information,dynamically,for,display,to,your,users,The,API,also,provides,methods,to,grant,and,remove,access,to,videos,on,your,website,based,on,a,user,s,unique,user,ID,Requests,are,returned,in,XML,or,JSON,format,An,API,key,is,required